":"2017-03-08T06:34:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>港鐵範圍內應該要有自己法律 不受SAR管轄<br />\n<br />\n車站衝鋒隊應該有自己法庭同監獄</blockquote><br />\nRailway Reich <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nThe Third Reich (地鐵-&gt;港鐵-&gt;港鐵帝國) <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote> <br />\nMetro Third Reich Corporation <br />\nThe fourth Reich Rail (TfR Rail) <br />\nMTR 2017 <br />\nMTR 2018: The Last Luggage <br />\n香港有 third/fourth rail 個名重靚"},{"pid":"6d17098d3cbc37962ba68480358a7d0ff18a14af","tid":146652,"uid":60545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-08T06:47:06.000Z","msg":"SS<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}